<HL>
   Pier 1 Imports Sales Increase
</HL>
<DATE>
05/17/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C10
</SO>
<CO>
   PIR
</CO>
<LP>
   FORT WORTH, Texas -- Pier 1 Imports Inc. said its sales in
the month ended May 5 rose 24.2%, to $43.3 million from $34.8
million a year earlier.
   The specialty retailer said that in the month sales at
stores open more than a year rose 8% from the year-earlier
level.
